title: Carleton to Host Storyboot School Graduation Ceremony (Carleton University)
text: ( Source : Carleton University ) Carleton University's Centre for Aboriginal Culture and Education (CACE), in partnership with Manitobah Mukluks, will be hosting the graduation ceremony for the Storyboot project on Wednesday, Oct. 14 , 2015 .
